channel.title: Fringe
channel.description:
Hello.. I just finished the final season of fringe. I just wanted to make a topic to see if any other fellow fringe fans out there are really bummed about the show stopping. It was my favourite show, and they just had to stop at season 5. Depressing... What was your favourite episode? I cannot say, every single one was good.
[b]***I really don't want haters here so if you have nothing to say.. don't say it. Fringe does not make sense without the story line, watch it season 1 through 5 and then tell me you don't like it.***[/b]
